Nissan to Introduce Seven New Electric Vehicles, Ghosn Says

-- B y   M a k i k o   K i t a m u r a
-- 
2011-06-27T06:31:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/nissan-to-introduce-seven-new-electric-vehicles-ghosn-says.html
Nissan Motor Co. plans to introduce
seven new electric vehicles after its Leaf, Chief Executive
Officer  Carlos Ghosn  said today in Yokohama.  Nissan and Renault will together aim to sell 1.5 million
electric vehicles in the six years to fiscal 2016, the automaker
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Makiko Kitamura in Tokyo at 
